# =============================================================================
# Chezmoi Ignore Patterns — AI-First Configuration
# =============================================================================
# Philosophy: Track EVERYTHING by default. Only exclude runtime caches,
# auth tokens, large binaries, and machine-specific ephemeral data.
#
# AI agent skills, rules, memories, workflows, agents.md, configs, and
# dotfiles are all first-class assets. They represent significant time
# investment and must be version controlled.
#
# Based on industry standards:
# - dotwee: One Skills Brain with chezmoi (DEV.to 2026)
# - BSWEN: Version Control AI Assistant Config (2026)
# - rymiwe: Claude Code Config Backup with chezmoi (GitHub Gist 2026)
# - chezmoi official docs: AI coding agent configuration (twpayne/chezmoi)
# =============================================================================

