# =========================================================================
# AI AGENT CONFIGURATION — WHAT TO EXCLUDE
# =========================================================================
# We track: skills, rules, memories, workflows, agents.md, configs,
#           instructions, prompts, commands, extensions, dotfiles
# We exclude: auth tokens, session data, caches, sqlite databases,
#             runtime state, large model caches
# =========================================================================

